{"type": "article", "id": 27932, "title": "制冰盒", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-08T07:24:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 65, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162336esOFRYvhQ6p2i78S.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>你是否也向往能在夏夜喝上一杯冰爽的饮料？来自台湾的 Jack Chu 和他的团队非常关注冰块对饮料的影响，他们为此专门设计出了一款可以在家使用的圆形制冰盒，取名为 Polar Ice Tray，让你仅靠家中冰箱就能制作出一款纯净的冰球。这个冰盒采用了分层设计，水从上至下一层层结冰，而空气则被挤压到底层，最终获得的就是一颗晶莹剔透的大冰球。当然你也可以发挥创意，用它将有趣的东西冻起来（比如一朵花）。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/polar-ice-tray-perfect-ice-for-the-perfect-drink--2#/\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 30 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162328BTaecyjYLF0CpZms.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.43548387\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162328VEgLZTXyiC24abQp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162329CFlWXEx2U4yDZYtv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43548387\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162330hweyuSjH72ZvrE9d.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41018519\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}